Report bugs to Arabeyes developers mailing list:
http://lists.arabeyes.org/mailman/listinfo/developer

Known issues:
=============

* Kerning is broken under Qt based applications and OpenOffice, both bugs
  were reported years ago and there is nothing we can do. Kerning issues was
  fixed in LibreOffice 3.4.
* Language specific features are only supported by Pango based applications.
